JUNE MEDICAL SERVICES L.L.C., et al., Petitioners
v.
Rebekah GEE, Secretary, Louisiana Department of Health and Hospitals No. 18-1323 Supreme Court of the United States. October 4, 2019

The petition for writ of certiorari is granted. The case is consolidated and a *36total of one hour is allotted for oral argument.
